(167, 1, '2017-05-17 02:59:37', '2017-05-17 02:59:37', 'Andrew was born and raised in South Eastern Pennsylvania. His first words, \"car keys\" made his interests evident and a ride in a Ferrari 328 GTS at the age of five defined his future. Needless to say, Andrew’s interest in cars was inevitable and extremely enthusiastic; which was the premise on which he and Adolfo founded LBI. Today he is an active, aggressive member of the team and collector car community.\r\n\r\nHe is constantly looking to grow, expand, educate himself (and others) all while enjoying the cars which he is so fortunate to be a part of every day. His areas of interest are certainly sports cars from the 1960’s, but he also has a great appreciation and understanding for Pre-War European and American classics. On the off chance you find Andrew not at the office or on the road in pursuit of the next find, you might find him on the lawn at Pebble Beach or Amelia Island with his family, or out on some back roads behind the wheel.', 'Andrew Mastin', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'andrew-mastin', '', '', '2017-05-19 05:32:05', '2017-05-19 05:32:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/lbi/?post_type=specialists&#038;p=167', 0, 'specialists', '', 0),
(168, 1, '2017-05-17 02:59:59', '2017-05-17 02:59:59', 'Adolfo is also a Pennsylvania native raised in the suburbs of Philadelphia. His interest in cars started at a young age when his father would take him to a local classic car dealership every Saturday morning. At age five, he could name the make and model of any car by looking at the front bumper.\r\n\r\nPresently, Adolfo is a recent Temple University graduate pursuing his long lived dream of turning his passion into a business at LBI. He also enjoys traveling the world, golf, tennis, and snowboarding. Adolfo specializes in post war sports cars with a concentration in Mercedes-Benz, Jaguar, Alfa-Romeo, and Austin-Healey. His early passion for cars has increased, and now serves as the foundation for LBI\'s creation, expansion, and recognition in the collector car market.', 'Adolfo Massari', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'adolfo-massari', '', '', '2017-05-18 20:50:33', '2017-05-18 20:50:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/lbi/?post_type=specialists&#038;p=168', 1, 'specialists', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2017-05-17 03:00:34', '2017-05-17 03:00:34', 'Diana is an enthusiastic member of LBI’s team. Assisting daily in our PR efforts as well as taking on the role of administrative assistant. A die-hard auto enthusiast, Diana’s passion carries over into her efforts here at LBI.\r\n\r\nShe is always there for the LBI team and is often the back bone of our office structure. Beyond LBI she is a loving mother of one, a very talented seamstress, home cook, licensed cosmetologist, and a “jack of all trades”.', 'Diana DuHaime', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'diana-duhaime', '', '', '2017-05-18 19:54:14', '2017-05-18 19:54:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/lbi/?post_type=specialists&#038;p=169', 3, 'specialists', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2017-05-17 03:00:56', '2017-05-17 03:00:56', 'Nick is originally from the Bethlehem Pennsylvania area where he was born and raised. He has been interested in cars since he was a small child but his passion really bloomed when he bought his first car and began to teach him self how to work on it. He now enjoys anything with wheels and a motor and loves learning everything he can about the world of classic cars and motorcycles.\r\n\r\nOn a day-to-day basis, Nick can be found doing a variety of things around the office. Ultimately though, he spends the majority of his time behind the lens of his camera photographing the various cars that make their way through the doors of the shop. He is a self-taught photographer and is always attempting to better his skills and learn more about the craft. Outside of the office he enjoys snowboarding, hiking, and working on his motorcycles.', 'Nick Zabrecky', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nick-zabrecky', '', '', '2017-05-18 19:54:38', '2017-05-18 19:54:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/lbi/?post_type=specialists&#038;p=170', 2, 'specialists', '', 0),
